{"tid":2291372,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"已經一年 仲係個世界到載浮載沉沉沉沉沉","createTime":"2020-11-18T16:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T18:51:00.000Z","uid":61927,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"156be523701ed31b2a564ba4d10bb8bbfac5755b","tid":2291372,"uid":61927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"一年前 感覺到自由係幾奢侈<br />\n一年前 感受到人心有幾脆弱<br />\n一年前 一齊立誓唔會再踏足呢個鬼地方<br />\n <br />\n由個刻開始所有野都唔同咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n失去左戰友 放棄左讀書 離開咗屋企人<br />\n原本以為好快就會曙光<br />\n一切都會慢慢變好<br />\n點知碌碌下ig原來已經一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一年過左了 <br />\n望住31號越黎越少人<br />\n望住輕裝到彩虹戰衣到真街坊<br />\n曾經年少輕狂嘅我以為狹路相逢勇者勝<br />\n以後一雙手可以握成拳頭能捱下去<br />\n慢慢只係感覺有心無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一年過左了<br />\n明明以前個個都話我好撚醒 以後大把前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣家日日返份牛工 收工就做成幾個鐘gym等屋企人瞓<br />\n費事面阻阻又嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原本有D父幹 衣家月月搵月月清<br />\n又睇唔到career path 又未搵到人生目標<br />\n放假就去搵啲手足老豆老母飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾家用變咗俾人地老豆老母可能我都係第一個<br />\n<br />\n呻完 共勉之<br />\n好鐘意一句 祝武運昌隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8444ba3ea1b8969713ed39b78a458ccca1dd982","tid":2291372,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:58:54.000Z","msg":"留住條命啦，德川家康都要長命過豐臣秀吉先贏"},{"pid":"675ead62497bb2744c9c9d1978fa84e19dd6bcf3","tid":2291372,"uid":61927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8444ba3ea1b8969713ed39b78a458ccca1dd982","tid":2291372,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:58:54.000Z","msg":"留住條命啦，德川家康都要長命過豐臣秀吉先贏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望快D見到希望 望住聽日班手足又上庭 又會心酸然後又默默咁生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b262a8f5c743c0eb8141205ef0adc95741107cdd","tid":2291372,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"675ead62497bb2744c9c9d1978fa84e19dd6bcf3","tid":2291372,"uid":61927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8444ba3ea1b8969713ed39b78a458ccca1dd982","tid":2291372,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:58:54.000Z","msg":"留住條命啦，德川家康都要長命過豐臣秀吉先贏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T17:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望快D見到希望 望住聽日班手足又上庭 又會心酸然後又默默咁生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T17:11:43.000Z","msg":"你要保重呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1694b07d621d18cf37f11672a18ebd84c8f12d6","tid":2291372,"uid":222513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T17:14:42.000Z","msg":"At least we have each other <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b268df89be105961688d63c120a93c49d99db63","tid":2291372,"uid":61927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1694b07d621d18cf37f11672a18ebd84c8f12d6","tid":2291372,"uid":222513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T17:14:42.000Z","msg":"At least we have each other <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T17:18:52.000Z","msg":"諗起冇咗自由 流亡他鄉嘅手足 我地仲有咩資格抱怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ab536f2da68981fb207c231c2dccde530fe4b1","tid":2291372,"uid":22341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T17:36:16.000Z","msg":"狹路相逢 勇者勝<br />\n<br />\n我地要做最堅定 最相信既一群<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2fc9174e911a5c6a3993a9f869dc5441f94f97","tid":2291372,"uid":365746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T18:08:54.000Z","msg":"手足，將來再聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d05fd85b30fac1167d8817db90310e720855de","tid":2291372,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"156be523701ed31b2a564ba4d10bb8bbfac5755b","tid":2291372,"uid":61927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"一年前 感覺到自由係幾奢侈<br />\n一年前 感受到人心有幾脆弱<br />\n一年前 一齊立誓唔會再踏足呢個鬼地方<br />\n <br />\n由個刻開始所有野都唔同咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n失去左戰友 放棄左讀書 離開咗屋企人<br />\n原本以為好快就會曙光<br />\n一切都會慢慢變好<br />\n點知碌碌下ig原來已經一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一年過左了 <br />\n望住31號越黎越少人<br />\n望住輕裝到彩虹戰衣到真街坊<br />\n曾經年少輕狂嘅我以為狹路相逢勇者勝<br />\n以後一雙手可以握成拳頭能捱下去<br />\n慢慢只係感覺有心無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一年過左了<br />\n明明以前個個都話我好撚醒 以後大把前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣家日日返份牛工 收工就做成幾個鐘gym等屋企人瞓<br />\n費事面阻阻又嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原本有D父幹 衣家月月搵月月清<br />\n又睇唔到career path 又未搵到人生目標<br />\n放假就去搵啲手足老豆老母飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾家用變咗俾人地老豆老母可能我都係第一個<br />\n<br />\n呻完 共勉之<br />\n好鐘意一句 祝武運